hero.name: ITACHI
hero.specialAbility:
SHARINGAN: The attack and defence values of enemy cards in combat are reduced by 1. 
Sharingan is Kekkei Genkai.
When your health ≤ 5 immediately find and activate SUSANOO card.

cards.title: Genjutsu: Sharingan
cards.immediateText:
Return your opponent's attack card to their hand. Look at their hand and choose an attack or versatile card for them to play. (It may be the 
same card).

cards.title: tsukuyomi
cards.afterText: Your opponent discards 1 random card. Add its BOOST value to this card's attack value.

cards.title: sharingan: copy jutsu
cards.basicText: This card's effects cannot be canceled.
cards.immediateText: Choose one of your opponent's cards that has no higher boost value (The card doesn't have to be Kekkei Genkai) and immediately play it instead of this one.

cards.title: Mirage Crow
cards.immediateText: If your opponent's card boost value is not greater, ignore all damage.
cards.afterText: If you have no damage move to any space in same zone.

cards.title: Enton: Amaterasu
cards.afterText: Your opponent may discard 1 card from their hand. If they don't ATK 3 Enton: Black fire.

cards.title: izanami
cards.basicText: Choose an opponent and look at their hand. Choose 2 card for them to discard. Gain 1 action.

cards.title: susanoo
cards.basicText:
Place card near.
Now you are SUSANOO.
You have permanent +3 bonus defence.
This card can't be discard by opponent !
At the start of your turn, you may return placed card to your hand.

cards.title: The Yata Mirror
cards.immediateText: Cancel all effects on your opponent's card.

cards.title: Totsuka no Tsurugi
cards.basicText: You can use this card only when activated SUSANOO.

cards.title: Katon: Hōsenka no Jutsu
cards.afterText: ATK 2 KATON: FLOW OF HOSENKA no JUTSU

cards.title: Bunshin Daibakuha
cards.afterText: If you lose deal 3 damage and move up by 3 spaces.

cards.title: Suiton: Suigadan
cards.afterText: If you win move target up by 1 space.

cards.title: Shurikenjutsu
cards.basicText: Deal 2 damage to every opponent's fighter  in same zone.

cards.title: Taijutsu: Hayanie
cards.afterText: Move to any spaces adjacent to target.
